{"Body":"<p>Aymara and Quechua have both topic and focus markers. There's a paper on the pragmatic suffixes in Aymara with a detailed explanation and many examples:</p>\n\n<p>Homola, Petr, and Matt Coler. 2013. “<a href=\"https://aclweb.org/anthology/W/W13/W13-3712.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pragmatic Structures in Aymara</a>.” In <em>Proceedings of the Second International Conference on Dependency Linguistics</em>, edited by Eva Hajičová, Kim Gerdes, and Leo Wanner, 98–107. Prague: MATFYZPRESS.</p>\n", "Id":"4405", "ParentId":"904", "LastEditorUserId":"444", "CreationDate":"2013-09-09T18:15:46.627", "OwnerUserId":"2451", "PostTypeId":"2", "comments":[], "LastEditDate":"2013-09-10T13:38:31.687", "LastEditedUser":{"UpVotes":"127", "WebsiteUrl":"", "Location":"Netherlands", "Id":"444", "DownVotes":"2", "AccountId":"902812", "Views":"19", "Reputation":"934", "CreationDate":"2011-10-23T14:14:27.380", "DisplayName":"arjan", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-14T14:07:55.473", "AboutMe":""}, "LastActivityDate":"2013-09-10T13:38:31.687", "Score":"3", "CommentCount":"1", "OwnerUser":{"UpVotes":"54", "Location":"Prague, Czech Republic", "DownVotes":"3", "Id":"2451", "ProfileImageUrl":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1", "AccountId":"935824", "Views":"11", "Reputation":"782", "CreationDate":"2013-09-09T18:11:01.840", "DisplayName":"Atamiri", "LastAccessDate":"2014-01-19T01:11:49.140", "Age":"36"}}